" Insert quotes around stuff
nnoremap <leader>" viwb<esc>i"<esc>ea"<esc>lel
nnoremap <leader>' viwb<esc>i'<esc>ea'<esc>lel
vnoremap <leader>" <esc>`<lt>i"<esc>`>la"<esc>
vnoremap <leader>' <esc>`<lt>i'<esc>`>la'<esc>

" \q to turn => () into => { return () }
noremap <leader>q ca({<CR>return <esc>p

" Quickly insert an empty new line without entering insert mode
nnoremap <Leader>o o<Esc>
nnoremap <Leader>O O<Esc>

" Remove arrow keys lol
nnoremap <Left> <nop>
vnoremap <Left> <nop>
inoremap <Left> <nop>
nnoremap <Up> <nop>
vnoremap <Up> <nop>
inoremap <Up> <nop>
nnoremap <Right> <nop>
vnoremap <Right> <nop>
inoremap <Right> <nop>
nnoremap <Down> <nop>
vnoremap <Down> <nop>
inoremap <Down> <nop>
